data.description: PRICE IMPROVED! **Rare find- single family home in the highly desirable neighborhood of Landsdowne conveniently located in major commuter routes of FFX county parkway, minutes to 2 metro stations, the beltway, Ft. Belvoir base, and just across from Wegmans grocery/Hilltop plaza/Landsdowne Center, and plenty of neighborhood restaurants to choose from.  This charming 3-bed, 2.5 bath is situated in a cozy cul de sac, fully fenced in back yard with a fuly finished basement that has a bonus room that can be used as a 4th bedroom or office space, plus a large Rec room and a rough-in plumbing ready for a 3rd bathroom, it also has a spacious laundry room and storage room. The main floor has hardwood floors throughout, a formal living room, formal dining, a separate family room with vaulted high ceiling and a fireplace. The Kitchen has brand new appliances, a breakfast room overlooking a beautiful and large patio deck area and spacious, flat backyard great for entertaining and relaxing.   3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs w/ new beautiful LVP floors, Primary bedroom has vaulted high ceiling with a completely updated en suite, the 2nd bathroom has brand new tile floors.  House is full of updates to enjoy:  *Brand New Windows throughout  *Brand new LVP floors throughout *Fresh paint throughout  *Brand new kitchen appliances *2 brand new ceiling fans *Roof (2years)  *HVAC/Water Heater (10-12 yrs.) *Newly stained patio deck.  The rest is up to your own style...This Landsdowne home is Move-in Ready, Don't miss out!
